akka.testkit.typed

Class BehaviorTestkit<T>

  • java.lang.Object
    • akka.testkit.typed.BehaviorTestkit<T>

  • public class BehaviorTestkit<T>
extends java.lang.Object
    Used for testing Behaviors. Stores all effects e.g. Spawning of children, watching and offers access to what effects have taken place.
